13 0 obj
<< /Length 1934 >>
stream
BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 106.8 610 Td (THE UNIQUE GRIEF OF LOSING A PARENT) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 40 600 m 392 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 580 Td (Losing a parent changes you at your core. It doesn't matter) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 565 Td (if you were 25 or 55 when it happened. Something fundamental) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 550 Td (shifts when the person who brought you into this world leaves it.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 535 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 520 Td (This grief is unique because:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 505 Td (- They knew you from your very beginning) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 490 Td (- They were your first model of love \(imperfect as it may have been\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 475 Td (- Part of your identity was built in relationship to them) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 460 Td (- You may now feel like an 'adult orphan' - untethered) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 445 Td (- Every milestone from now on will have their absence) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 430 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 415 Td (This journal is for you to:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 400 Td (- Process the waves of grief as they come) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 385 Td (- Preserve memories before they fade) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 370 Td (- Say the things left unsaid) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 355 Td (- Find ways to carry their love forward) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 340 Td (- Give yourself permission to grieve YOUR way) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 325 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 310 Td (There is no timeline for this. There is no 'getting over it.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 295 Td (There is only learning to carry this love-turned-grief) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 280 Td (alongside everything else in your life.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 265 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 250 Td (Write when you're ready. Skip days when you're not.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.5 Tf 40 235 Td (This journal will wait for you.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
